<chapter line="1">Ekaṭhānikādiyamakagāthā</chapter>
<hangnum line="2" number="101"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="3">Ākaṅkhakkhākaṅkhaṅga kaṅkhāgaṅgākhāgahaka,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="4">Kaṅkhāgāhakakaṅkhāgha hā hā kaṅkhā kahaṃ kahaṃ.</gathalast>
<hangnum line="5" number="102"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="6">Appagabbho apagabbho amoho mā pamohako,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="7">Maggamukhaṃ mokhamāha māhā mohamūhakkhamaṃ.</gathalast>
<hangnum line="8" number="103"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="9">Pāpāpāpabhavaṃ passaṃ pāpāpabhavuggato,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="10">Pāpāpāpabhavāsaṅgā pāpāpāpabhavāgato.</gathalast>
<hangnum line="11" number="104"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="12">Kusalākusalaṃ passaṃ kusalākusalaṃ caji,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="13">Kusalākusalāsaṅga kusalākusalā cuto.</gathalast>
